gmd:title.gco:CharacterString: Navy Global Environmental Model (NAVGEM), 0.5 degree, 2013-present, 500 hPa Height, Lon+/-180

gmd:abstract.gco:CharacterString: Navy Global Environmental Model (NAVGEM) is a global numerical weather prediction computer model. It replaced NOGAPS as the prime model in the middle of February 2013 at the Navy Fleet Numerical Meteorology and Oceanography Center (FNMOC) Weather model synoptic site. [Wikipedia]
